"title": "4060: nature",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4060: nature",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's creation, often with special reference to plant and animal life.</p>\n<h2>Nature is God's creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:11\">PSA 89:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:12\">ISA 45:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:5\">JER 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24\">ACT 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:6\">REV 10:6</a></p>\n<h3>Plants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:4-Gen2:9\">GEN 2:4–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14-Ps104:16\">PSA 104:14–104:16</a></p>\n<h3>Land and sea</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1\">PSA 24:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:9-Gen1:10\">GEN 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4-Job38:11\">JOB 38:4–38:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:12\">ISA 40:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:8\">AMO 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:9\">JON 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>The sun, moon and stars</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:9\">JOB 9:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14-Gen1:18\">GEN 1:14–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3\">PSA 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:3-Ps148:5\">PSA 148:3–148:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:35\">JER 31:35</a></p>\n<h3>Animals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:22\">GEN 1:20–1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:7-Job12:10\">JOB 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:25\">PSA 104:25</a></p>\n<h3>Human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:11\">EXO 4:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:12\">ISA 45:12</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6\">PSA 95:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:3\">PSA 100:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:2\">PRO 22:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:5\">JER 27:5</a></p>\n<h2>The distinction between humanity and the rest of nature</h2>\n<h3>God created human beings alone in his image</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:10\">COL 3:9–3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1\">GEN 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9\">JAS 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Humanity is the steward of nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:16\">PSA 115:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:26–1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">GEN 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:5-Ps8:8\">PSA 8:5–8:8</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in nature</h2>\n<h3>In sustaining nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:6\">LUK 12:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:1-Ps147:17\">PSA 147:1–147:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24-Acts17:28\">ACT 17:24–17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:17\">COL 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>In providing for plant life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:4\">LEV 26:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:29\">MAT 6:28–6:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:27\">LUK 12:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:25\">JOB 38:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14-Ps104:16\">PSA 104:14–104:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:6-Jonah4:10\">JON 4:6–4:10</a></p>\n<h3>In the elements and seasons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:10\">JOB 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:27\">JOB 36:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:11-Job37:13\">JOB 37:11–37:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a></p>\n<h2>God makes himself known through the natural order</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:24-Job36:26\">JOB 36:24–36:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1-Ps8:4\">PSA 8:1–8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:3\">PSA 19:1–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15-Acts14:17\">ACT 14:15–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24-Acts17:28\">ACT 17:24–17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:21\">ROM 1:18–1:21</a></p>",
